description:
The youngest of the sisters. This 20-years-old prodigy on programming wants to create her own IT company. Albeit regarding herself as the coolest one, her logical way of thinking interferes with her social life. Because she is the youngest one of the sisters when their mother died, she is the most in need of a maternal figure in her life.
Source: http://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Watanuki-san_Chi_No
name: Watanuki Mitsuki
